original: Åberg, Thure Emanuel Kristoffer, komminister, Vamlinigbo, f. 24/10/91 i Huskvarna av Aug. Å. o. Fredrika Göransson. G. 17 m. Elis’abeth Johansson. Barn: Lennart f. 18, Aina 19, Maj 2:2, Carin 26. — Prästv. f. Visby stift 28. Varit v. domkyrkokommin. i Visby, v. pastor samt tf. kyrkoh. i Vamlingbo, kommin. i Vamlingbo fr. 3!7.
translated: Aberg, Thure Emanuel Kristoffer, vicar, Vamlingbo, b. 24/10/91 in Huskvarna to August A. and Fredrika Göransson. Married on 17/xx to Elis'abeth Johansson. Children: Lennart b. 18, Aina b. 19, Maj b. 2:2, Carin b. 26. Ordained as a priest in Visby Cathedral in 1928. Has been an assistant vicar in Visby, pastor, and acting incumbent in Vamlingbo, and vicar in Vamlingbo since 1937.
